---
const painPoints = [
  {
    icon: `<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>`,
    heading: 'Decisions made on gut feel',
    body: 'The numbers are always late, always somewhere else, always incomplete. So you make expensive calls based on feel.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>`,
    heading: 'AI sounds great in theory',
    body: 'You keep hearing about AI and what it can do. But when it comes to your business, it just feels complicated and out of reach.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>`,
    heading: 'Jobs that bleed money silently',
    body: 'By the time anyone notices a job went wrong, the margin is gone. Nobody saw it coming because nobody had a clear view.',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-brand-surface">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Heading -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="section-label">The problem</p>
      <h2 class="font-poppins font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl text-brand-text max-w-xl leading-tight">
        Sound familiar?
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Pain point cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {painPoints.map((point) => (
        <div class="bg-brand-bg rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="text-brand-accent mb-5" set:html={point.icon} />
          <h3 class="font-poppins font-semibold text-lg text-brand-text mb-3">
            {point.heading}
          </h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-brand-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            {point.body}
          </p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Closing statement -->
    <div class="border-t border-brand-surface3 pt-12">
      <p class="font-poppins font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-text max-w-2xl">
        The real cost is not the chaos.
        <span class="text-brand-accent"> It is the decisions you are making blind.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
